about.summary: A Python toolkit for performing searches with the RCSB Protein Data Bank (PDB) using its XML-based API.

name: pypdb
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pypdb" %}
{% set version = "1.200" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/46/07/bf5f570b52f43b94fdb02c1d779feb5fd1e9535d0b4a6e9701b8f15038cc/pypdb-1.200.tar.gz
  md5: 5061452bb58bc765a5037317402736ec

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - xmltodict
    - beautifulsoup4
    - matplotlib
    - urllib3
    - jsonschema

test:
  imports:
    - pypdb

about:
    home: http://www.wgilpin.com/pypdb_docs/html/
    license: MIT
    license_family: MIT
    license_file: LICENSE.txt
    summary: A Python toolkit for performing searches with the RCSB Protein Data Bank (PDB) using its XML-based API.
    dev_url: https://github.com/williamgilpin/pypdb

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - tsenapathi
